videos.description: Trae Young can't keep control of the ball and Kansas State's Barry Brown takes advantage and hits two easy baskets in the first half.
videos.headline: Kansas State capitalizes on Young's back-to-back turnovers

videos.description: Cartier Diarra intercepts the Sooners' ball and speeds down the court for an explosive finish in the first half.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Diarra steals and scores

videos.description: Trae Young drives and gets past Kansas State defenders for a nice layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Young drives for early bucket

videos.description: Trae Young keeps the ball alive and finally knocks in a 3-pointer from the left wing with less than 10 minutes left in the first half.
videos.headline: Young hits first triple

videos.description: Trae Young misses a free throw but gets his own offensive board and knocks one in from deep.
videos.headline: Young gets own rebound and hits 3

videos.description: Khadeem Lattin feeds Trae Young who banks in a nice layup.
videos.headline: Lattin finds Young for layup

videos.description: Rashard Odomes sends a nice bounce pass to Trae Young who hits a layup and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Young creates 3-point play

videos.description: Trae Young gets after it and hits an easy jumper from inside the paint.
videos.headline: Young gets to basket for nice finish

videos.description: Trae Young drives through traffic for a tricky layup and appears to make contact with Xavier Sneed after the basket but there is no foul.
videos.headline: Young banks a tough layup, avoids foul

videos.description: Cartier Diarra connects with Xavier Sneed who rises up and jams it in to extend the Wildcats' lead to 62-50.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Diarra hits Sneed for the alley-oop slam

videos.description: Trae Young speeds to the inside for a nice layup making him the quickest player to reach 500 points in Sooners' history
videos.headline: Young gets 500th career points

videos.description: Kansas State celebrates after Dean Wade drills a triple to extend the Wildcats lead to 85-67 with less than one minute left in the game against the Sooners.
videos.headline: Wade knocks down dagger 3-pointer

videos.description: Kansas State celebrates with fans in the bleachers after the Wildcats upset the No. 4 Sooners 87-69 on Tuesday night.
videos.headline: Team joins fans in stands after victory

videos.description: Barry Brown scores 24 points and credits his teammates for stopping Trae Young and the Sooners in Tuesday night's victory.
videos.headline: Brown prepared for Young

videos.description: Trae Young scores 20 points on 8-of-21 shooting but turns the ball over 12 times as No. 4 Oklahoma falls to Kansas State 87-69.
videos.headline: Off night for Young leads to Sooners' loss

videos.description: Seth Greenberg breaks down some of Trae Young's struggles in the Sooners' loss to Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Young should make simpler plays) 2018/01/16 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Young should make simpler plays

videos.description: Trae Young turns the ball over a Big 12-record 12 times in No. 4 Oklahoma's 87-69 loss against Kansas State.

videos.headline: Young struggles in historically bad performance
